      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues] Line 76: Call reconnection is now gated on both originalPriority and priority because isCallNotification already requires remoteMessage.priority \u003d\u003d PRIORITY_HIGH. FCM can downgrade delivered priority while originalPriority remains HIGH, so an incoming call push originally sent as high priority may skip connectivityChanged() and risk timing out after sleep. Split call-type detection from priority gating and use originalPriority consistently for this decision.\n```suggestion\n        val isCallPush \u003d pushType.contains(\"audioCall\") || pushType.contains(\"videoCall\")\n        val isCallNotification \u003d isCallPush \u0026\u0026 remoteMessage.originalPriority \u003d\u003d RemoteMessage.PRIORITY_HIGH\n```\nThen keep the later condition as `if (isCallNotification \u0026\u0026 !isAppInForeground())`.",
